## Ignore build artifacts and temporary files
**/bin/
**/obj/
**/.vs/
**/.vscode/
**/.idea/

## Ignore test results
**/TestResults/
**/*.trx
**/coverage.*.xml
**/coverage.*.json

## Ignore user-specific files
*.user
*.suo
*.userosscache
*.sln.docstates

## Ignore package directories
**/packages/
**/node_modules/

## Ignore database files
*.db
*.db-shm
*.db-wal
*.sqlite
*.sqlite3

## Ignore logs
*.log
**/logs/

## Ignore OS specific files
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
*.swp
*~

## Ignore environment files
.env
.env.local
.env.*.local

## Git files
.git/
.gitignore
.gitattributes
.gitflow

## Documentation and misc
*.md
LICENSE
docs/
*.yml
*.yaml
!appsettings*.json

## CI/CD
.github/
.gitlab-ci.yml
azure-pipelines.yml

## Docker files (except necessary ones)
docker-compose*.yml
Dockerfile.*
!Dockerfile

## Frontend build artifacts (if any)
**/wwwroot/dist/
**/wwwroot/lib/
**/ClientApp/dist/
**/ClientApp/node_modules/